summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the sale and conveyance to M. A. Segale, Inc., a Washington corporation, of certain City (Lighting Department) property in the Southeast quarter of the Northeast quarter of Section 26, Township 23 North, Range 4, E.W.M., in King County, Washington.
note: Conformed copy of Ordinance 105206 obtained from City Law Department on January 26, 1979. Original checked out by the Law Department September 30, 1977.
